Class TGNavigationFragment

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.arch.lifecycle.LifecycleOwner, android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, TGPauseNavFragment.Container, TGNavInfoBar.Container

    public class TGNavigationFragment
extends TGBaseMapFragment
implements TGPauseNavFragment.Container, TGNavInfoBar.Container
    An implementation of TGBaseMapFragment that allows for full functionality of turn-by-turn navigation. This Fragment can be used in conjunction with TGMapFragment to create a fully functional navigation and search application. The parent fragment or activity should implement TGNavigationFragment.Container in order to be informed of actions related to this Fragment
